        <item>
            <title>2.8.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[Two new characters — Anay and Shikhar — join the lineup (24 to choose from). And your pet's controls now live on the pet itself: right-click your own pet for Hide, Roaming, Cursor mode, and Character. The menu-bar icon stays for friends, updates, and settings.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 11:23:43 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.8.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.8.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
