        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.7.2</title>
            <description><![CDATA[New: Reset Pat… (start over). Right-click the menu-bar 🐱 → "Reset Pat…" to remove yourself and all your friendships and begin fresh with a new pet — a clean way to start over or hand the app to someone else.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 02:48:20 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.7.2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.7.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
