        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.7.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[Friends stay in sync more reliably. Fixed a bug where a friend could show as "napping/away" while they were actually online (a clock-difference between Macs), and your pets now reconnect on their own after a Wi-Fi blip — no relaunch needed. Added a ↻ Refresh button in the Friends window to re-sync on demand.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 02:29:53 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.7.1</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.7.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
