        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.7.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[New cursor mode: <b>Chipkoo</b> 🫶 — your pet clings to the cursor and follows it everywhere, until someone pats it. Set it from the menu-bar → Cursor. It works with friends too: your clinging pet hops onto their cursor, and a pat from anyone gently lets it go.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 01:20:41 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.7.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.7.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
