        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.6.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[Reliability hardening for friends, verified by an exhaustive multi-device test suite (70 end-to-end checks): unfriending no longer pings every other person's app, and your friend graph stays perfectly in sync across everyone, all the time.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jun 2026 00:03:47 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.6.1</sparkle:version>
