        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.6.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[Friends, in perfect sync. Adding a friend now shows up on both desktops instantly — no restart. Their mood and character (and yours) update live across every friend, you can paste an invite code, and your character pick during setup applies right away.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 22:51:08 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.6.0</sparkle:version>
