        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.5.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[Smoother Push: your pet now flees the cursor in a smooth, continuous glide and slides along walls instead of darting around. No more erratic movement.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 22:24:45 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.5.1</sparkle:version>
