        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.5.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[Pat is now always free-flowing — she follows or flees your cursor and you drag her anywhere. New "Keep roaming" toggle lets her wander the whole screen (corners, middle, edges). Push & Attract now work at a comfortable close range, and she can never get trapped in a corner.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 22:16:03 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.5.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.5.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
