        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.4.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<b>Pets play with your cursor.</b> Pick a Cursor mode — Attract (your pet comes to your cursor), Push (it flees), or Neutral. Your mode syncs to friends, so their pet on your desktop reacts to your cursor too. Right-click → Cursor.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 21:52:07 +0530</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2.4.0</sparkle:version>
