        </item>
        <item>
            <title>2.3.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[Reliability pass: fixed a bug that kept friends' live moods from syncing, kept your friends from vanishing on a network blip, and tidied the app. Add a friend and you'll see each other change in real time.]]></description>
            <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 17:28:33 +0530</pubDate>
