        <item>
            <title>2.3.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<b>Friends, reimagined.</b> No more rooms or codes — just add a friend with an invite, and your pixel selves live on each other's desktops, always there, changing with your day. Private by design (only friends see you).]]></description>
