        <item>
            <title>2.2.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<b>Friends are real pets now.</b> Bring a friend onto your desktop and they're a full Digital Pat — blinking, reacting, changing with their day — and you can pat them just like your own. Simpler and cuter.]]></description>
