            <title>2.1.1</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<b>The Room is a hangout now.</b> Friends sit together as a cute group — tap one to bring them onto your desktop, then pat them (💗) and poke them just like your own pet. Cleaner Room, simpler everything.]]></description>
