        <item>
            <title>2.1.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<b>Rooms, refined.</b> Friends now live in the Room — pull the ones you want onto your desktop (your "deck"), drag them around, and poke each other right where they are. Switch rooms anytime. Simpler, cuter, and the room-empties bug is fixed.]]></description>
